findings.title: Owner can change Uniswap router address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the Uniswap router address.

findings.title: Owner can remove sniper account
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to remove a sniper account.

findings.title: Owner can enable and disable sniper protection
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to enable or disable sniper protection, which could lead to potential security risks if misused.

findings.title: Owner can change max wallet size
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum wallet size, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing address.

findings.title: Owner can add multiple exclusions to address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to add multiple exclusions to an address, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner Can Change Fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change reflect, marketing, burn and liquidity fees which can lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change liquidity and marketing ratio
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the liquidity and marketing ratio, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses from fees.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: Potential denial-of-service vulnerability due to block gas limit, which could lead to OUT_OF_GAS exceptions.
